\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><html lang=\"es\"><header class=\"bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/es\"><img src=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-5.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink\" class=\"h-10 w-auto\"/></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8\"><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/es\">Inicio</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/es/solutions\">Soluciones</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/es/services\">Servicios</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/es/about\">Nosotros</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/es/contact\">Contacto</a><a class=\"bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] transition-colors\" href=\"/es/contact\">Solicitar Demo</a><a class=\"text-[#686868] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"https://app.safetylink.ai\">Ingresar</a><a class=\"text-xs text-navy font-semibold bg-[#eef3ff] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/en\">EN</a></nav><button class=\"lg:hidden text-navy p-2\" aria-label=\"Menu\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"bg-navy text-white py-20 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4\">Safety Link: La Plataforma de Seguridad Más Legalmente Defendible</h1><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 italic max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Proteja a su gente, su negocio y su futuro — sin costos inflados ni incertidumbre.</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] shadow-[0_2px_6px_0_rgba(0,183,55,0.25)] transition-all \" href=\"/contact\">Consulta Gratuita</a></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Guiados por ex-liderazgo de OSHA e impartido por capacitadores autorizados por OSHA</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Bilingüe (inglés/español) por defecto — plataforma, contenido y soporte</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Programas específicos por sitio (no plantillas genéricas) – políticas adaptadas a cada lugar de trabajo</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Documentación legalmente defendible, asesorada por abogados de OSHA</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Mobile-first + modo offline – auditorías, inspecciones, fotos, GPS, marcas de tiempo sin internet</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Precio PyME con potencia empresarial – cumplimiento escalable y accesible</div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Capacidades Integradas (Listas para Usar)</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">LMS Integrado (SCORM 1.2)</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Cursos interactivos basados en roles con exámenes y certificados</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Bilingüe completo</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Interfaz, contenido y soporte en inglés y español</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Políticas por sitio</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Políticas a nivel cliente/sitio, control de versiones, acuses</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Firmas digitales</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Registros listos para auditoría, exportables</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Automatización CAPA</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Seguimiento, fechas límite, evidencia de corrección, escalamiento</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Dashboards en tiempo real + IA</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Alertas de capacitación vencida, fallas, CAPAs abiertas, tendencias</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Portal de contratistas</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Permisos por rol y sitio, separación de funciones</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Modo offline mobile-first</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Funcionalidad completa sin señal</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Precio PyME</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Precios escalonados, capacidad empresarial cuando se necesita</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-2\">Comparación: Safety Link vs Herramientas Genéricas</h2><p class=\"text-primary text-center font-semibold mb-8 italic\">Otras herramientas marcan casillas. Nosotros eliminamos riesgos.</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b-2 border-navy\"><th class=\"text-left py-3 text-navy\">Feature</th><th class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">Other Tools</th><th class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">Safety Link</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Bilingüe (EN/ES) por defecto</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Programas por sitio</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Capacitadores autorizados OSHA</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Ex-liderazgo OSHA en staff</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Soporte experto y consultas</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Documentación legalmente defendible</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Soporte de auditoría en sitio</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Accesible para PyMEs</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Dos Modalidades</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]\"><div class=\"h-40 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/software-tablet-BSMxY2uI.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Software de Seguridad</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-4\">Capacitación, auditorías, incidentes, CAPA, registros OSHA y analítica en una sola plataforma. Diseñado para PyMEs que buscan control sin hojas de cálculo.</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] shadow-[0_2px_6px_0_rgba(0,183,55,0.25)] transition-all \" href=\"/contact\">Explorar Software</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]\"><div class=\"h-40 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/program-team-BDtLA316.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Gestión de Programas</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-4\">Profesionales autorizados por OSHA diseñan e implementan programas específicos por sitio, realizan auditorías, capacitan equipos y lo mantienen listo para inspección.</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-white text-navy px-9 py-3.5 rounded-[10px] font-medium text-sm shadow-[rgba(0,0,0,0.3)_0px_0px_1px_0px] hover:shadow-md transition-all \" href=\"/safety-program-management\">Explorar Gestión de Programas</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Qué Hace de Safety Link el Estándar de Oro</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">1</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Experiencia Autorizada por OSHA</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Ex-liderazgo de OSHA y abogados laborales guían la plataforma; firmas de supervisor y registros de auditoría completos.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">2</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Arquitectura de Proceso Primero</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Cada módulo (inducción → capacitación → CAPA) está interconectado para que nada quede fuera.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">3</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Evidencia Integrada</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Geo-etiquetado, marcas de tiempo, políticas con control de versiones, firmas electrónicas e informes listos para auditor.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">4</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Rendimiento en Campo</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Móvil responsive, modo offline, captura de foto/video, GPS, firmas digitales.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">5</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Escala Sin Sobresaltos</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Comience a escala PyME; agregue supervisión multi-sitio, controles de contratistas y analítica avanzada.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Destacados de Funcionalidades</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_5_feature-mobile-BeQJutVM.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Mobile + Offline</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Acceda a herramientas de seguridad en cualquier lugar, sin internet</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_6_feature-audits-Chwoapsm.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Auditorías e Inspecciones</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Auditorías en tiempo real, seguimiento de hallazgos</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_7_feature-training-DlajBew5.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Capacitación (SCORM)</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">LMS completo con soporte de cursos SCORM bilingües</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_8_feature-quizzes-BN4TbLCR.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Exámenes y Certificados</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Verifique comprensión, genere certificados automáticamente</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/feature-policies-q899d3JL.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Políticas por Sitio</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Adaptadas a sus riesgos y ubicaciones</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_10_feature-workflow-CfUrGWrp.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Flujo de Acciones Correctivas</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Seguimiento de problemas desde identificación hasta resolución</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_11_feature-dashboard-H-FS-km3.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Dashboards de Cumplimiento</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Visibilidad en tiempo real del desempeño de seguridad</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_12_feature-contractor-CBU_fgsQ.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Portal de Contratistas</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Permisos basados en roles para trabajadores externos</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_13_feature-affordable-DzRtQ8Ac.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Accesible para PyMEs</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Funcionalidades empresariales sin precio empresarial</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-10\">Cómo Funciona</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold\">1</div><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Evaluar y Auditar</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">Revisiones bilingües específicas por sitio descubren riesgos antes que OSHA.</p></div><div><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold\">2</div><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Implementar</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">Construya su programa en inglés/español, active capacitación y flujos de trabajo.</p></div><div><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold\">3</div><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Monitorear y Mejorar</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">Dashboards, alertas IA, CAPA y registros lo mantienen listo para inspección.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Diseñado para PyMEs y Empresas de Alto Riesgo</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-48 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_14_smb-teamwork-BfplCzdt.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Equipos PyMEs</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm\">Seguridad nivel empresarial sin grandes facturas. Lance rápido, gestione simple.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-48 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/enterprise-growth-CxBH0X1y.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Empresas de Alto Riesgo</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm\">Controles multi-sitio, analítica avanzada, supervisión de contratistas, evidencia lista para litigios.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-10\">Seguridad que Mueve los Números</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2\">15–35%</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">menos lesiones con programas IIPP bien implementados</p></div><div><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2\">$170B+</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">costo anual de lesiones en EE.UU. – proteja su P&amp;L</p></div><div><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2\">Hasta 6×</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">ROI en inversiones de seguridad</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-8\">Industrias que Servimos</h2><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3\"><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Manufactura</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Construcción</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Salud y Hospitales</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Energía y Servicios / Petróleo, Gas</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Gobierno y Sector Público</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Transporte y Logística</span></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4\">¿Listo para proteger a su gente y su negocio?</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-lg mb-8\">Hable con un Asesor Autorizado por OSHA</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] shadow-[0_2px_6px_0_rgba(0,183,55,0.25)] transition-all \" href=\"/contact\">Solicitar Demo</a></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10\"><div><img src=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-1.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink\" class=\"h-8 w-auto mb-4\"/><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4\">La única plataforma de cumplimiento de seguridad legalmente defendible respaldada por ex-liderazgo de OSHA y expertos en derecho laboral. Protegiendo fuerzas laborales con capacitación, auditorías y soluciones de cumplimiento bilingües.</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 italic\">SafetyLink no está afiliado ni respaldado por OSHA. El apoyo consultivo es proporcionado por ex-liderazgo de OSHA.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Enlaces Rápidos</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/es/solutions\">Soluciones</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/es/services\">Servicios</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/es/contact\">Contacto</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/es/privacy-policy\">Política de Privacidad</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"https://app.safetylink.ai\">Ingresar</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Cumplimiento y Confianza</h4><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2\"><p>Safety Link, LLC</p><p>111 Congress Ave, Suite 500</p><p>Austin, Texas 78701</p><p class=\"pt-2\">888-373-7822</p><p>833-780-0728</p><p>compliance@safetylink.ai</p><div class=\"flex gap-1 items-center pt-2 text-xs text-primary\"><span>✓</span> OSHA Authorized Trainers</div><div class=\"flex gap-1 items-center text-xs text-primary\"><span>✓</span> SOC 2 Compliant</div></div></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] px-6 py-6\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-gray-400\"><p>© 2026 SafetyLink. Todos los derechos reservados. Soluciones de cumplimiento de seguridad legalmente defendibles.</p><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/es/privacy-policy\">Política de Privacidad</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/es/terms-of-service\">Términos de Servicio</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/es/accessibility\">Accesibilidad</a></div></div></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--></html><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3z5q_p4msz2ha.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n7:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\na:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\nc:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\ne:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/305zfmpkz2n9r.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/cf514f5d0007dafa-s.p.1wc2mf9hp9pav.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\